I"Ä<p>You just need to choose a template like the <a href="http://localhost:4000/design/page/"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">page</code></a>- or <a href="http://localhost:4000/design/page-fullwidth/"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">page-fullwidth</code></a>-template and then just use <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">{% include gallery %}</code>.
<!--more--></p>

